{"tid":1322472,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一個幾句屌黑警口號","createTime":"2019-07-16T02:56:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T03:34:26.000Z","uid":4322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fc3370526a4674154a4b3f9987a3c47aefea6aa9","tid":1322472,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T02:56:26.000Z","msg":"當日發夢有幸係新城市一齊屌走班黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n千人齊用 黑警 屌你老母 不停屌<br />\n但同友人討論過後 略嫌未夠誅心<br />\n因為佢地應該對咒罵麻木咗<br />\n所以可以向行為或身份認同方面著手<br />\n而且一齊屌要有氣勢 二至四字最適合<br />\n<br />\n如果下次有類似情形 多人對少人<br />\n以下係小弟愚見 可以用：<br />\n自盡！<br />\n自轟！<br />\n投降！<br />\n棄械！<br />\n棄卒！<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d7598769fcdb0d0df9d937256732d58bc16d063","tid":1322472,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:00:46.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"bf2d2e47b17f8b3b1206590124d68557d348b5b1","tid":1322472,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:00:56.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"17de8173305b5696b45e99c16a77edf27ea3fa97","tid":1322472,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:06:00.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"f0e8ad38f40e703be7db88749cc3774be7ba1dd5","tid":1322472,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:06:13.000Z","msg":"Condom仔！"},{"pid":"930584311a7113734b859c353180f61d4e76e237","tid":1322472,"uid":144883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:08:01.000Z","msg":"嗌口號好攰啫，你唔知最新撐警手勢咩<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/af/Ringvinger.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fa%2Faf%2FRingvinger.jpg&h=c9561a95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74f3135cc9344a8f0302844558251e1ecf88cb26","tid":1322472,"uid